<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior batcave evening}
<A>__{tight on a tiny electronic device: two cylindrical steel casings bracketed together, topped by a digital timer. bruce makes a few adjustments with a jeweler's screwdriver, hits a trigger, and watches the timer tick off seconds. 30.}
<L>__{29. 28. at 25 seconds, bruce kills the}
<A>__{countdown and clamps the device into an empty packet on his utility belt. he stands up wearily. he's in his bat suit, minus the cape and cowl. behind him, hanging back discreetly in the shadows, is his loyal butler alfred.}
